<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 12:58:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>揭开人类发育的秘密：早期神经细胞选择如何塑造周围神经系统</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/unlocking-secrets-of-human-development-how-early-nerve-cell-choices-shape-the-peripheral-nervous-system</link><description>我们的身体中有数百万个神经元分支，使它们与我们的大脑保持密切沟通。随着生长中胚胎的细胞就位并发挥其特殊作用，这种外围网络早在出生前就开始形成。人类发育的这一关键阶段无法直接监测，但通过检查成体细胞中残留的遗传线索，科学家们现在对周围神经系统的发育起源有了令人惊讶的见解。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/unlocking-secrets-of-human-development-how-early-nerve-cell-choices-shape-the-peripheral-nervous-system3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 12:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/unlocking-secrets-of-human-development-how-early-nerve-cell-choices-shape-the-peripheral-nervous-system</guid></item><item><title>机器人中的人工智能代理完全按照专家的警告行事</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-agent-in-a-robot-does-exactly-what-experts-warned</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 12:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-agent-in-a-robot-does-exactly-what-experts-warned</guid></item><item><title>多发性骨髓瘤细胞在免疫治疗后适应，有助于解释为什么许多患者复发</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/multiple-myeloma-cells-adapt-after-immunotherapy-helping-explain-why-many-patients-relapse</link><description>多发性骨髓瘤是成人中第二常见的血液癌症。它始于白细胞，负责产生帮助身体抵抗感染的抗体。一旦骨髓瘤细胞开始繁殖，血细胞就更难正常发挥作用。多发性骨髓瘤有有效的治疗方法，包括可以显着延长生存期的免疫疗法；然而，在某些情况下，癌细胞会对治疗产生耐药性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/multiple-myeloma-cells-adapt-after-immunotherapy-helping-explain-why-many-patients-relapse2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 12:28:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/multiple-myeloma-cells-adapt-after-immunotherapy-helping-explain-why-many-patients-relapse</guid></item><item><title>ForSight 表示已完成首例全机器人白内障手术</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/forsight-says-it-completed-first-fully-robotic-cataract-surgery</link><description>ForSight Robotics 表示，它已经完成了世界上首例完全由机器人辅助的人类白内障手术，该手术使用了其专有的 JASPER 平台，该公司表示，该手术可能标志着在扩大全球眼科手术覆盖范围方面迈出的重要一步。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/forsight-says-it-completed-first-fully-robotic-cataract-surgery.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 12:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/forsight-says-it-completed-first-fully-robotic-cataract-surgery</guid></item><item><title>破碎的恒星揭示了黑洞如何点燃万亿级太阳耀斑</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/shredded-stars-reveal-how-black-holes-ignite-trillion-sun-flares</link><description>超大质量黑洞是宇宙中最神秘的物体之一。它们的重量通常是太阳质量的数百万甚至数十亿倍，并且位于大多数大型星系的中心。银河系的中心坐落着人马座 A*，这是我们银河系的超大质量黑洞，质量约为 400 万个太阳。但这些黑洞不发光，因此天文学家只能通过它们对附近恒星和气体的影响来间接探测它们。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/shredded-stars-reveal-how-black-holes-ignite-trillion-sun-flares.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 11:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/shredded-stars-reveal-how-black-holes-ignite-trillion-sun-flares</guid></item><item><title>仔细研究免疫“记忆”可能会促进对抗致命疾病的进展</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/taking-a-closer-look-at-immune-memory-could-spur-progress-in-the-fight-against-lethal-illnesses</link><description>人类平均拥有约 1.8 万亿个免疫细胞。这些细胞在体内巡逻，寻找细菌、病毒、癌症和其他威胁。疫苗通过教导我们的免疫细胞针对特定病原体来增强这一安全系统。据世界卫生组织称，疫苗诱导的免疫力每分钟可挽救约 6 条生命。但这种保护性免疫“记忆”能持续多久？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/taking-a-closer-look-at-immune-memory-could-spur-progress-in-the-fight-against-lethal-illnesses.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 11:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/taking-a-closer-look-at-immune-memory-could-spur-progress-in-the-fight-against-lethal-illnesses</guid></item><item><title>AI 如何努力解决简单的 ARC-AGI 基准挑战问题的示例</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/an-example-of-how-ai-struggles-to-solve-a-simple-arc-agi-benchmark-challenge-question</link><description>背景：OpenAI 最近推出了两种新的人工智能模型， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/an-example-of-how-ai-struggles-to-solve-a-simple-arc-agi-benchmark-challenge-question2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 11:28:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/an-example-of-how-ai-struggles-to-solve-a-simple-arc-agi-benchmark-challenge-question</guid></item><item><title>深部脑刺激和低强度聚焦超声神经调节的转化前景：IFCN 手册章节</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/translational-prospectives-for-deep-brain-stimulation-and-low-intensity-focused-ultrasound-neuromodulation-ifcn-handbook-chapter</link><description>[IFCN 手册章节：DBS 和聚焦超声神经调节] Neumann 和 Darmani：“在本书章节中，我们回顾了最近出现或即将实现飞跃的新兴创新，改善了脑部疾病患者的治疗。” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/translational-prospectives-for-deep-brain-stimulation-and-low-intensity-focused-ultrasound-neuromodulation-ifcn-handbook-chapter2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 11:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/translational-prospectives-for-deep-brain-stimulation-and-low-intensity-focused-ultrasound-neuromodulation-ifcn-handbook-chapter</guid></item><item><title>EB 病毒单核细胞增多症导致 MS 风险显着增加</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ms-risk-upped-significantly-with-ebv-mononucleosis</link><description>一项新的回顾性研究显示，实验室确诊的 Epstein-Barr 病毒阳性传染性单核细胞增多症 (EBV-mono) 与未感染 EBV-mono 的患者相比，患多发性硬化症 (MS) 的风险高出三倍多。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ms-risk-upped-significantly-with-ebv-mononucleosis.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 10:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ms-risk-upped-significantly-with-ebv-mononucleosis</guid></item><item><title>心率变异性调节人类特质焦虑与交感神经活动之间的关联</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/heart-rate-variability-moderates-the-association-between-trait-anxiety-and-sympathetic-nerve-activity-in-humans</link><description>一项新的研究挑战了长期存在的观点，即阿尔茨海默病主要由淀粉样蛋白斑块驱动，而是指出神经元内部存在微妙但关键的竞争。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/heart-rate-variability-moderates-the-association-between-trait-anxiety-and-sympathetic-nerve-activity-in-humans2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 10:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/heart-rate-variability-moderates-the-association-between-trait-anxiety-and-sympathetic-nerve-activity-in-humans</guid></item></channel></rss>